telemetry/evaluation/EVAL-primitive-tools/run-g1-smoke-2026-04-28/
telemetry/evaluation/EVAL-primitive-tools/run-g3-full-fre283-2026-04-28/
telemetry/evaluation/EVAL-primitive-tools/run-g3-full-fre283-budget50-2026-04-28/
telemetry/evaluation/EVAL-primitive-tools/run-g3-full-sonnet-2026-04-28/

